- Audio in all sections of *History Tracers*;
- Addition of the [Physics](https://historytracers.org/index.html?page=physics), [Chemistry](https://historytracers.org/index.html?page=chemistry), and [Biology](https://historytracers.org/index.html?page=biology) sections;
- Improvements to JavaScript code, taking another step toward transforming the project into a tool for audio creation;
- Inclusion of Indigenous families in the [Family Tree](https://historytracers.org/index.html?page=families) section;
- New content in the [First Steps](https://historytracers.org/index.html?page=first_steps) sections;
- Fixes for various bugs.
